{"tid":736260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲打屋企人有儲物購物癖","createTime":"2018-07-10T06:10:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T06:10:07.000Z","uid":191504,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6e5192bda555101e7517b39c4949237ac1c83a7a","tid":736260,"uid":191504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T06:10:07.000Z","msg":"屋企人有儲物購物癖真係好慘<br />\n一屋都係雜物 梳化無位坐 飯枱食唔到飯<br />\n80年代買落嘅書有曱甴蛋都唔肯掉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瘋狂買廚具電器但又唔會用<br />\n唔常用嘅野就算收入閣樓 之後都會因為搵唔到而再買過<br />\n叫佢掉野好似要佢命咁 話無用過就掉好浪費<br />\n叫佢租迷你倉又會話啲野要隨時攞到先屬於自己<br />\n行出行入就算打側身都不斷撞到野<br />\n仲要不斷係Facebook啲page訂收納箱/收納工具 妄想用完啲野就會整齊哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}